metadata.name: Birth of Venus Moment_30 #03/20
metadata.description:
Video still from the music video „Birth of Venus". 
This artwork is part of the Ping Pong Project which involves a series of physically existing sculptures, music videos that provide the sculpture with an interpretative framework and stills taken from the video.

The video stills come in limited editions of 20. One edition will be reserved for the artist. 

Please also see the music video „Birth of Venus", length 01:33 min (language: French), limited edition of 100.

The physical sculpture „Adler" (Eagle), 3 D print, dimensions: 15 x 23 x 30 cm is available upon request.
